properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 9 at 2:51PM AKST until February 10 at 6:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Wet snow expected. Total snow accumulations of up to 6
inches. Winds gusting as high as 50 mph.

* WHERE...Klondike Highway near White Pass.

* WHEN...From 5 AM to 6 PM AKST Monday. Heaviest snowfall in the
late morning.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Areas of blowing
snow could significantly reduce visibility. The hazardous
conditions could impact travel.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 5 AM TO 6 PM AKST MONDAY ALONG KLONDIKE HIGHWAY NEAR WHITE PASS
